* {{a|slang}} [[hasta la vista]], [[hasta la vista, baby]], [[later]], [[laters]], [[keep it real]], [[peace out]]. [[take it easy]], [[toodles]], [[peace]], [[cya]]
* {{a|UK, informal}} [[cheerio]], [[cheery-bye]], [[toodle pip]] {{a|dated}}
